ComplexEvaluator
public class ObjectEvaluator<DATA,DATA_VARIABLE,USER_DATA_TYPE>
extends java.lang.Object

Evaluates a given expression (as String or ASTNode) into a DATA object type. For example the ComplexEvaluator class uses the Complex class data type.

See Also:
ComplexEvaluator, Complex
